-- Finmeccanica to Bid for Brazilian Warship Contract, Il Sole 24 Ore Reports
-- Tommaso Ebhardt
-- 2010-07-17T10:08:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-17/finmeccanica-to-bid-for-brazilian-warship-contract-il-sole-24-ore-reports.html

          
          
             Finmeccanica SpA  is preparing a bid
with Fincantieri SpA for a 5 billion-euro ($6.5 billion) order
from Brazil to supply nine warships and other vessels, Il Sole
24 Ore reported, without saying where it got the information.  
 Finmeccanica and Fincantieri must present their bid for the
order by Aug. 15, the Italian daily said.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
